<plot>This is the tale of the world's most misunderstood creatures - the Angelenos. This tongue-in-cheek documentary explores the Angelenos' mission: to create entertainment that will brighten the common folks' drab lives! Created entirely from stock footage and film clips with the tone of a 1950s-era educational film, this tale explores how entertainment is created; from its stars to its studio executives; and finds out why Angelenos are so uniquely suited to this calling. This satire takes a look at a world that's begging to be spoofed!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?583051</url></doc>
